responseId":"064e36748395d45b52f755c3fe99a09c"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionyyvvze0yvf2s1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🎲 最新双色球开奖结果：\n\n==================================================\n📅 2026-05-07 | 期号: 2026051\n   🔴 红球: 09 14 15 16 29 30 | 🔵 蓝球: 10\n--------------------------------------------------\n📅 2026-05-05 | 期号: 2026050\n   🔴 红球: 06 09 25 27 28 30 | 🔵 蓝球: 03\n--------------------------------------------------\n📅 2026-05-03 | 期号: 2026049\n   🔴 红球: 03 04 14 15 18 20 | 🔵 蓝球: 02\n--------------------------------------------------\n📅 2026-04-30 | 期号: 2026048\n   🔴 红球: 09 15 18 24 28 33 | 🔵 蓝球: 01\n--------------------------------------------------\n📅 2026-04-28 | 期号: 2026047\n   🔴 红球: 07 16 21 24 27 30 | 🔵 蓝球: 07\n--------------------------------------------------"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778320251177},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"数据获取并存储成功了！我来给用户总结一下结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **双色球最新开奖号码已获取并存储到数据库！**\n\n---\n\n🎲 **最新一期（第2026051期）**\n- 📅 开奖日期：2026-05-07\n- 🔴 红球：**09 14 15 16 29 30**\n- 🔵 蓝球：**10**\n\n---\n\n📊 **最近5期开奖记录：**\n\n| 期号 | 日期 | 红球 | 蓝球 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| 2026051 | 05-07 | 09 14 15 16 29 30 | 10 |\n| 2026050 | 05-05 | 06 09 25 27 28 30 | 03 |\n| 2026049 | 05-03 | 03 04 14 15 18 20 | 02 |\n| 2026048 | 04-30 | 09 15 18 24 28 33 | 01 |\n| 2026047 | 04-28 | 07 16 21 24 27 30 | 07 |\n\n---\n\n💾 **数据库信息：**\n- 共存储 **6027** 条历史开奖记录\n- 数据库路径：`skills/double-color-ball/data/double_color_ball.db`\n\n需要我帮你分析这些数据或者生成预测号码吗？🍀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":556,"output":320,"cacheRead":51515,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52391,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778320251178,"responseId":"064e367bb500746fed664bce79949337"},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50c439bae0a0b4899e6e5eb2883\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-09 18:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50c439bae0a0b4899e6e5eb2883]\nhaidong: 大乐透技能，获取一下最新开奖号码并存储到数据库中。"}],"timestamp":1778321273630},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求使用大乐透技能获取最新开奖号码并存储到数据库。让我先读取大乐透技能的SKILL.md来了解如何使用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2snpakf5wexo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":52364,"output":103,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52467,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778321273634,"responseId":"064e3a7a68eaebe44b900f21de8ec3a8"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2snpakf5wexo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: super-lotto\ndescription: 大乐透历史数据抓取、存储和分析技能。用于查询彩票500万网站、抓取历史开奖数据（前区红球+后区蓝球）、存储到本地数据库、进行数据分析和频率统计、生成号码预测。触发词：大乐透、彩票、开奖、彩票预测、历史数据、中奖号码、彩票分析、超级大乐透、大乐透预测。\n---\n\n# 大乐透数据抓取与分析预测\n\n## 概述\n\n此技能提供大乐透历史开奖数据的抓取、存储、查询分析和号码预测能力。支持从彩票500万网站抓取历史数据，存储到本地SQLite数据库，提供频率分析、热冷号统计，并基于多种策略生成预测号码。\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 1. 初始化数据库（首次使用）\n\n```bash\npython scripts/init_db.py\n```\n\n### 2. 抓取历史数据\n\n```bash\npython scripts/fetch_history.py\n```\n\n### 3. 生成预测\n\n```bash\n# 生成所有策略的预测（推荐）\npython scripts/predict.py\n\n# 查看详细统计\npython scripts/predict.py --stats\n\n# 生成3组热号策略预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy hot --count 3\n\n# 使用最近50期数据预测\npython scripts/predict.py --history 50\n```\n\n### 4. 查询数据\n\n```bash\n# 查看最新10期开奖\npython scripts/query.py latest\n\n# 查看最新50期\npython scripts/query.py latest 50\n\n# 号码频率分析\npython scripts/query.py analyze\n```\n\n## 预测模型\n\n### 预测策略\n\n| 策略 | 说明 | 适用场景 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 🔥 热号策略 | 选择历史出现频率最高的号码 | 追热号 |\n| ❄️ 冷号策略 | 选择历史出现频率最低的号码 | 追冷号 |\n| 📈 遗漏策略 | 选择很久未出现的号码 | 追遗漏 |\n| ⚖️ 均衡策略 | 热号+冷号+遗漏混合 | 平衡风险 |\n| 🤖 ML加权策略 | 频率40%+遗漏60%加权评分 | 智能推荐 |\n\n### 预测命令\n\n```bash\n# 生成1组预测（默认所有策略）\npython scripts/predict.py\n\n# 生成5组热号预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy hot --count 5\n\n# 生成5组冷号预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy cold --count 5\n\n# 生成5组遗漏策略预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy missing --count 5\n\n# 生成5组均衡策略预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy balanced --count 5\n\n# 生成5组ML加权策略预测\npython scripts/predict.py --strategy ml --count 5\n\n# 显示详细统计信息\npython scripts/predict.py --stats\n\n# 使用最近100期数据预测\npython scripts/predict.py --history 100\n```\n\n## 使用场景\n\n### 场景1：获取最新预测\n\n用户：\"大乐透预测\"\n\n操作步骤：\n1. 运行 `python scripts/predict.py`\n2. 选择喜欢的策略组合\n\n### 场景2：查看统计信息\n\n用户：\"分析一下大乐透的热号冷号\"\n\n操作步骤：\n```bash\npython scripts/predict.py --stats\n```\n\n会输出：\n- 前区号码频率柱状图 TOP 10\n- 后区号码频率柱状图\n- 遗漏排行榜（前区）\n\n### 场景3：抓取最新数据\n\n用户：\"帮我更新大乐透数据\"\n\n操作步骤：\n```bash\npython scripts/fetch_history.py\n```\n\n## 大乐透规则\n\n- **前区（红球）**：从 01-35 中选择 5 个不重复的号码\n- **后区（蓝球）**：从 01-12 中选择 2 个号码\n- **开奖频率**：每周一、三、六\n\n## 数据源\n\n### 彩票500万网\n\n- **URL**: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\n- **优势**: 数据准确，更新及时\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│ 初始化数据库 │ → python scripts/init_db.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  抓取数据    │ → python scripts/fetch_history.py\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │\n       ▼\n┌─────────────┐\n│  预测分析    │ → python scripts/predict.py\n└─────────────┘\n```\n\n## 脚本说明\n\n### predict.py（新增）\n\n- 基于历史数据的多策略预测模型\n- 支持5种预测策略\n- 生成频率统计和遗漏分析\n- 后区号码智能推荐\n\n### init_db.py\n\n- 初始化SQLite数据库\n- 创建表结构和索引\n\n### fetch_history.py\n\n- 使用Playwright从彩票500万网站抓取数据\n- 支持增量更新\n\n### query.py\n\n- 提供多种查询功能\n- 支持频率分析\n\n## 数据库表：lottery_records\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| id | INTEGER | 主键 |\n| issue_number | TEXT | 期号（如 26048） |\n| draw_date | DATE | 开奖日期 |\n| front_ball_1~5 | INTEGER | 前区号码（1-35） |\n| back_ball_1~2 | INTEGER | 后区号码（1-12） |\n\n## ⚠️ 免责声明\n\n彩票开奖是完全随机的概率事件，历史数据分析和任何预测模型都无法保证中奖。本技能提供的预测仅供参考娱乐，请理性购彩，量力而行。\n\n## 与双色球的区别\n\n| 彩票类型 | 前区（红球） | 后区（蓝球） |\n|---------|------------|------------|\n| 双色球 | 6个（1-33） | 1个（1-16） |\n| 大乐透 | 5个（1-35） | 2个（1-12） |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778321278717},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经了解了大乐透技能的使用方法。现在需要：\n1. 初始化数据库（如果需要）\n2. 抓取最新数据\n3. 查看最新开奖结果\n\n让我执行这些步骤。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来帮你获取大乐透最新开奖号码并存储到数据库。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sjhk4gmx21iy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && python scripts/init_db.py 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1761,"output":147,"cacheRead":51963,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53871,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778321278718,"responseId":"064e3a7f2eb49e6b543335c7c802d534"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sjhk4gmx21iy_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ 数据库初始化成功: /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/data/super_lotto.db"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"✅ 数据库初始化成功: /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/data/super_lotto.db","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778321284233},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"数据库初始化成功，现在抓取历史数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_udtlbhxfcr7y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && python scripts/fetch_history.py 2>&1","timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":110,"output":79,"cacheRead":53755,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53944,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778321284234,"responseId":"064e3a847f27fffadd5636beab6d79f2"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_udtlbhxfcr7y_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"============================================================\n🎲 大乐透历史数据抓取\n============================================================\n\n📡 正在访问彩票500万网...\n   URL: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\n📊 正在解析数据...\n✅ 成功抓取 30 条记录\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py:155: DeprecationWarning: The default date adapter is deprecated as of Python 3.12; see the sqlite3 documentation for suggested replacement recipes\n  cursor.execute('''\n✅ 数据保存完成: 新增 0 条, 更新 30 条\n\n✅ 总计保存 30 条记录"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":495,"aggregated":"============================================================\n🎲 大乐透历史数据抓取\n============================================================\n\n📡 正在访问彩票500万网...\n   URL: https://datachart.500.com/dlt/history/newinc/history.php\n📊 正在解析数据...\n✅ 成功抓取 30 条记录\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/fetch_history.py:155: DeprecationWarning: The default date adapter is deprecated as of Python 3.12; see the sqlite3 documentation for suggested replacement recipes\n  cursor.execute('''\n✅ 数据保存完成: 新增 0 条, 更新 30 条\n\n✅ 总计保存 30 条记录","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778321288100},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"数据抓取完成，成功抓取了30条记录。现在查看最新开奖结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_okvnw1602m12_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto && python -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nconn = sqlite3.connect('data/super_lotto.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\ncursor.execute('SELECT issue_number, draw_date, front_ball_1, front_ball_2, front_ball_3, front_ball_4, front_ball_5, back_ball_1, back_ball_2 FROM lottery_records ORDER BY draw_date DESC LIMIT 5')\nrows = cursor.fetchall()\nprint('🎱 最新大乐透开奖结果：\\n')\nprint('='*55)\nfor row in rows:\n    issue = row[0]\n    date = row[1]\n    front = [row[2], row[3], row[4], row[5], row[6]]\n    back = [row[7], row[8]]\n    front_str = ' '.join(f'{n:02d}' for n in sorted(front))\n    back_str = ' '.join(f'{n:02d}' for n in sorted(back))\n    print(f'📅 {date} | 期号: {issue}')\n    print(f'   🔴 前区: {front_str} | 🔵 后区: {back_str}')\n    print('-'*55)\nconn.close()\n\"\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":331,"output":336,"cacheRead":53755,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54422,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778321288101,"responseId":"064e3a8808b8cf3e6bf340429bbbe383"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_okvnw1602m12_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🎱 最新大乐透开奖结果：\n\n=======================================================\n📅 2026-05-06 | 期号: 26049\n   🔴 前区: 01 06 14 15 17 | 🔵 后区: 02 03\n-------------------------------------------------------\n📅 2026-05-04 | 期号: 26048\n   🔴 前区: 11 17 20 23 35 | 🔵 后区: 01 10\n-------------------------------------------------------\n📅 2026-05-02 | 期号: 26047\n   🔴 前区: 09 20 21 23 28 | 🔵 后区: 06 11\n-------------------------------------------------------\n📅 2026-04-29 | 期号: 26046\n   🔴 前区: 01 13 18 27 33 | 🔵 后区: 04 07\n-------------------------------------------------------\n📅 2026-04-27 | 期号: 26045\n   🔴 前区: 01 15 21 26 33 | 🔵 后区: 04 07\n-------------------------------------------------------"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":26,"aggregated":"🎱 最新大乐透开奖结