{"traceSchema":"openclaw-trajectory","schemaVersion":1,"traceId":"afc80ba3-c1f2-4cfa-924c-f5504e228303","source":"runtime","type":"trace.artifacts","ts":"2026-05-09T10:26:31.232Z","seq":6,"sourceSeq":6,"sessionId":"afc80ba3-c1f2-4cfa-924c-f5504e228303","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","runId":"b9949a53-f2a7-4eea-a8a0-3605640e6e01","workspaceDir":"/workspace/projects/workspace","provider":"coze","modelId":"auto","modelApi":"openai-completions","data":{"capturedAt":"2026-05-09T10:26:31.232Z","finalStatus":"success","aborted":false,"externalAbort":false,"timedOut":false,"idleTimedOut":false,"timedOutDuringCompaction":false,"promptErrorSource":null,"usage":{"input":98600,"output":34231,"cacheRead":2067405,"total":2200236},"promptCache":{"lastCallUsage":{"input":499,"output":509,"cacheRead":104827,"cacheWrite":0,"total":105835},"lastCacheTouchAt":1778322380184},"compactionCount":0,"assistantTexts":["好的，我来一次性完成所有优化建议的实现。先看一下当前技能结构：","好的，我来系统性地实现所有优化建议。先看一下现有的脚本结构：","\n现在开始实现所有优化建议。我将创建一个完整的升级脚本：","现在运行升级脚本：","有个语法错误，让我修复：","问题是Python代码在heredoc中被错误解析了。让我分步创建文件：","现在更新SKILL.md版本号并进行验证：","现在验证所有新功能：","需要重新创建文档：","现在进行最终验证并生成报告：","Shell脚本有语法问题，让我检查并修复：","所有验证通过！现在生成最终报告：","---\n\n## ✅ v5.1.0 升级完成 - 全部验证通过\n\n### 📊 实现的功能\n\n| 优先级 | 功能 | 文件 | 验证 |\n|--------|------|------|------|\n| 🔴 P0 | **一键自动修复** | `scripts/one-click-fixer.sh` | ✅ |\n| 🔴 P0 | **批量检查功能** | `scripts/batch-scan-v2.sh` | ✅ |\n| 🟠 P1 | **CIS合规检测** | `rules/cis/*.yaml` (11个) | ✅ |\n| 🟠 P1 | **Agent自动修复** | `agent/auto_fixer_agent.py` | ✅ |\n| 🟠 P1 | **详细修复指南** | `docs/DETAILED_FIX_GUIDE.md` | ✅ |\n| 🟡 P2 | **钉钉兼容性** | `agent/dingtalk_compat.py` | ✅ |\n\n### 📁 新增文件\n- **脚本**: 2个 (batch-scan-v2.sh, one-click-fixer.sh)\n- **Python**: 2个 (auto_fixer_agent.py, dingtalk_compat.py)\n- **CIS规则**: 11个\n- **文档**: 2个 (DETAILED_FIX_GUIDE.md, CHANGELOG-v5.1.0.md)\n\n### ✅ 语法验证\n- 所有 Shell 脚本通过 `sh -n` 检查\n- 所有 Python 脚本通过 `py_compile` 检查\n\n### 📈 反馈来源\n| 用户 | 建议 |\n|------|------|\n| @Dragon_626032f | 一键自动修复功能 |\n| @tanger-pm | 批量检查功能、文档详细化 |\n| @红黄绿的黄 | CIS Benchmark合规检测 |\n| @道之动 | Agent模式自动修复、钉钉兼容性 |\n| @旺财 | 文档完善 |\n\n### 📌 快速使用\n\n```bash\n# 一键自动修复所有问题\nbash scripts/one-click-fixer.sh --auto\n\n# 批量检查多个Agent\nbash scripts/batch-scan-v2.sh --agents agent1,agent2\n\n# Agent模式自动修复\npython3 agent/auto_fixer_agent.py --list\n```\n\n需要我帮你提交到GitHub或上传到虾评平台吗？🍀"],"finalPromptText":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50c4d27eb8b4b28a2f3e071787b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-09 18:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50c4d27eb8b4b28a2f3e071787b]\nhaidong: 把全部的优化建议一次性执行升级，现在就做。做完要验证，保证修改的正确性。","itemLifecycle":{"startedCount":51,"completedCount":51,"activeCount":0},"toolMetas":[{"toolName":"read","meta":"first 100 lines of /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/healthcheck/SKILL.md"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"find files named \"*.sh\" in /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/healthcheck -> show first 50 lines, `find /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/healthcheck -type f -name \"*.sh\" -o -name \"*.py\" -o -name \"*.md\" 2>/dev/null …`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"list files in /workspace/projects/extensions/ -> show first 20 lines, `ls -la /workspace/projects/extensions/ 2>/dev/null | head -20`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"find files named \"*healthcheck*\" in /workspace/projects, `find /workspace/projects -type d -name \"*healthcheck*\" 2>/dev/null`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"list files in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/, `ls -la /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"show /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md -> show first 15